Release 0.5 (in development)
----------------
# added ability to provide detailed validation error information using DetailedError exceptions

Release 0.4
----------------
* added support to python 3.7, 3.8 and 3.9
* added support to django 3.0, 3.1 and 3.2
* removed support to python 3.6
* removed support to django 2.1


Release 0.3.4
-------------
* Add related_no_serialized_fields handling to mixin
* Pass request in context to nested related
* Standardize setup for libraries
